query:
SELECT eq.id, eq.examId, eq.questionId, eq.points, q.type, q.question 
FROM examQuestions eq 
LEFT JOIN questions q ON eq.questionId = q.id 
WHERE eq.examId IN (SELECT id FROM exams WHERE title LIKE '%工務%') 
LIMIT 10
